features: PERFECT CHOICE FOR YOUR NEEDS - ADBAOBO mini thermal printer seems to be a better choice for company business, work plans, office assistant, study notes, photo printing for travel, memos, meeting notes, and shopping lists. Its portability and convenience make it a great tool for on-the-go printing needs. Suitable for office, students, amateur archivists, treasure moms etc. Absolutely! This mini portable printer would indeed be ideal for gifts during Back to School, Children's Day, Halloween, Thanksgiving, Christmas, birthday and other special occasions.

MINI BLUETOOTH PRINTER - Bluetooth 2.1/4.2 connection allows for wireless printing, with one-click printing saves time and effort, allowing users to print photos and text instantly without ink and toner. This not only reduces printing costs but also offers a more convenient printing experience. This feature makes the printer a versatile and user-friendly option for various printing needs. Note: Please follow the printer's user manual to search "Tiny Print" on the App Store or on Google to connect and use.

SMART AI FEATURES - By integrating AI painting technology into the printer APP, you can utilize the AI Painting feature to artistically process images before printing, transforming them into various styles of artwork, ranging from cartoonish to line art styles, and even generating unique artwork based on key descriptions. This intelligent painting feature provides users with more personalized and diverse printing options, while also enhancing the artistic and creative aspects of printed works.

INSTANT PRINTING & POWERFUL APP - The "Tiny Print" app's variety of free features, including web printing, document printing, and character recognition, provides a range of options for creative and practical printing needs. Additionally, the availability of free fun materials, sticky note templates, to do lists, and label templates makes it a comprehensive tool for various printing tasks. ADBAOBO X6 tiny printer is designed for printing, it does not have camera functionality. Note: Choosing deep printing is clearer. If printing is blank, check if the printing paper is loaded upside down.

POCKET STICKER PRINTER - 3.3*3.3*1.7 Inch, about 0.37 lb weight, easy to slip into a pocket or bag. Sticker printer machine is built in a rechargeable battery, standby for at least 1 week after a full charge. Portable Wireless Printers is easy to print anytime, anywhere. CONVENIENT FUN STICKY PAPERS - X6 sticker maker includes one roll of 57mm adhesive sticky paper(already put into the mini printer), allows it to be cut the printouts into labels of any shape and size using scissors, you can use it to create festive stickers, DIY projects and other creative designs to add unique and thoughtful to all celebrations.
